<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I would say start with V. honestly. It&apos;s his first novel. The seeds of everything he does subsequently in his career have their foundation there. It&apos;s<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I would say start with V. honestly. It's his first novel. The seeds of everything he does subsequently in his career have their foundation there. It's one of the finest first novels ever written, maybe the single finest.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
