<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/691614-what-is-the-significance-of-the">What is the significance of the &quot;...?&quot; that punctuates the majority of Dixon&#39;s conversation?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_691614'><a id="like_count_community_question_691614" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/691614?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F413.Mason_Dixon">like</a></span>

