<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/34543971-miroslaw-aleksander"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/34543971-miroslaw-aleksander">Miroslaw Aleksander</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Dixon speaks in Geordie, so this is probably a mark of exaggerated up-speak and meter of speech (this is my somewhat-educated guess))
</span>
</div>
